</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field--2 field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><h2 style="text-align: right;"><u><span style="color:#b22222;">➔ </span><a href="http://e-info.org.tw/taxonomy/term/46567"><span style="color:#b22222;">看更多2016十大環境新聞</span></a></u></h2>
