</ul></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field--2 field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><h2 style="text-align: right;"><u><span style="color:#b22222;">➔ </span><a href="http://e-info.org.tw/taxonomy/term/46567"><span style="color:#b22222;">看更多2016十大環境新聞</span></a></u></h2>
</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-14 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/229">海洋</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-10 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/16">回顧與前瞻</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-25 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/46567">2016十大環境新聞回顧</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/10157">海洋油污</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/1147">漏油</a></div></div></div><div id="block-views-author-block" class="block">
