</ul><h2><span style="color:#0000cd;">電子垃圾鑽漏洞跨國收受 公益機構也涉案</span></h2>
<div class="align-center">
<figure class="image"><a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/basel-action-network/26313129403/in/album-72157668235322295/"><img alt="在香港新界發現的戴爾廢螢幕，直接暴露在戶外。圖片來源：baselactionnetwork（CC BY-NC-ND 2.0）" height="571" src="https://c2.staticflickr.com/8/7509/26313129403_b53cf12190_b.jpg" width="851" /></a>
