</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-14 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/229">海洋</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/108">政策</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-10 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/16">回顧與前瞻</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-25 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/43700">2015回顧</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/2234">捕鯨</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/43727">海保署</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/42747">海岸管理法</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/1755">海洋保護區</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/43726">海洋委員會</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/2198">魚翅</a></div></div></div><div id="block-views-author-block" class="block">
      <h2 class="block-title">作者</h2>
    <div class="field-items">
     
              
    <div class="content clearfix">
    <a href="/node/200001" title="彭瑞祥" class="author-link">彭瑞祥</a>
