		<a href="http://e-info.org.tw/taxonomy/term/17917">PX</a></li>
<li>
		<a href="http://e-info.org.tw/taxonomy/term/43441">開放資料</a><br />
		 </li>
</ul><p class="rtecenter"><a href="https://e-info.neticrm.tw/civicrm/contribute/transact?reset=1&amp;id=59" style="text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(9, 112, 167); line-height: 20.4px;"><img alt="捐款支持環境資訊中心，加入打造優質環境媒體的行列！" src="http://e-info.org.tw/files/19770154572_cacbbafb55_z_0.jpg" style="width: 640px; height: 64px;" title="捐款支持環境資訊中心，加入打造優質環境媒體的行列！" /></a></p>
</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-14 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/196">公害汙染</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/199">廢棄物</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/198">水汙染</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/197">空氣汙染</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-10 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/16">回顧與前瞻</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-25 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/43700">2015回顧</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/43223">2015高雄氣爆週年</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/43586">土壤污染</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/1439">水汙染防治</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/41930">空氣污染</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/43441">開放資料</a></div></div></div><div id="block-views-author-block" class="block">
      <h2 class="block-title">作者</h2>
    <div class="field-items">
     
              
    <div class="content clearfix">
    <a href="/node/200003" title="陳文姿" class="author-link">陳文姿</a>
