    <div class="content clearfix">
    <a href="/node/200004" title="洪鬱婷" class="author-link">洪鬱婷</a>
      <div class="field field-name-field-photo field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/node/200004"><img src="http://e-info.org.tw/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/29733787122_1a33afa44c_o.jpg?itok=bAsIRUt0" width="220" height="220" alt="" /></a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>環保不只是一種生活風格，而是一種普世價值，比如說人權、自由和平等。</p>
